text: "Positions" (stylized in as "positions") is a song by Ariana Grande from her album Positions (album). It was released on October 23, 2020, by Republic Records. It reached the top of the Billboard Hot 100. It is Grande's fifth US number-one single. == References == Category:2020 songs Category:Ariana Grande songs Category:Billboard Hot 100 number one songs
title: Positions (song)
